{"tid":1092884,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"創紀錄！BLACKPINK新歌〈Kill This Love〉勇奪美國iTunes排行榜第一名，連歐美粉絲都瘋狂！","createTime":"2019-04-05T07:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T10:45:14.000Z","uid":58335,"like":23,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f11c59a369f3a18c3f935c3d5b32426bf6f2da11","tid":1092884,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T07:57:04.000Z","msg":"bp大發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等睇你班傻子又屈bp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK新歌真的重播一百遍也不會膩！<br />\n<br />\nYG 高人氣女團 BLACKPINK 自 2016 年出道一路紅到現在，更是美國《告示牌》百大單曲榜史上成績最高的韓國女團。粉絲們敲碗期待已久的最新迷你專輯終於在今天正式推出，之前所釋出的全員新造型中，Jennie 一頭金髮就已經引起網友們熱烈討論，終於等到了首支主打單曲〈Kill This Love〉MV 正式曝光，才上架短短三小時就締造了超過 500 萬的觀看次數，強烈的曲風加上個性的舞蹈和視覺效果，讓人聽一次就上癮！BLACKPINK 這首單曲更登上美國 iTunes 排行榜第一名，創紀錄成為首支登上榜首的亞洲女子團體，更是繼天命真女（Destiny's Child）後第二支登上首位的女子團體。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O8Jv5Oe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO8Jv5Oe.jpg&h=c4d025c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cosmopolitan.com/tw/entertainment/celebrity-gossip/gmp27045458/blackpink-new-track-kill-this-love/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com%2Ftw%2Fentertainment%2Fcelebrity-gossip%2Fgmp27045458%2Fblackpink-new-track-kill-this-love%2F&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=48ee769c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cosmopolitan.com/tw/entertainment/celebrity-gossip/gmp27045458/blackpink-new-track-kill-this-love/</a>"},{"pid":"76341b4cf1ed1aace0a7c6eda806471a19587ea4","tid":1092884,"uid":165368,"like":19,"dislike":8,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:17:50.000Z","msg":"今次真係大巴大巴打落傻仔酸民度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed0a82951